Package edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model.rdf

Contains the Apache RDF implementation of the common model interfaces and some utility classes

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RdfBackend
    The RdfBackend interface used to generate data sets from Strings and Strings from data sets.
    RdfTransactionExecuter
    Base interface for RdfTransactions
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RdfAnnotation
    The RdfAnnotation implementation with RDF commons as data backend
    RdfAnnotationList
    The RdfAnnotationList implementation
    RdfContainer
    Implements a Container with RDF commons as data backend
    RdfModelFactory
    The RdfModelFactory implementation.
    RdfOutputContainer
    The class is used to generate the correct output representation of the Container.
    RdfPage
    Implements a Page with RDF commons as data backend
    RdfUtilities
    Utility class with common operations on graphs and datasets
    RdfWapObject
    Basic RdfWapObject implementing all common functionality of Annotations and Containers.
